# Frontend Testing

## Component test coverage

- Every route-facing component file must have a corresponding test file.
- Prefer colocated naming, for example:
  - `src/components/routes/health/PingView.tsx`
  - `src/components/routes/health/PingView.test.tsx`

## Rule intent

- Changes to route component behavior should include or update the matching component tests.
